  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Welcome to the Future of Anti-Gravity Racing</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the cockpit of next-generation anti-gravity ships. In a world where speed rules all, only the fastest can claim glory in the Millennium Cup. Get ready for a high-stakes ride through stunning sci-fi tracks and intense team rivalries.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3582420/extras/8882fb319c1660d2e8a08c66e688b4ca.avif?t=1770201688\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3582420/extras_big/8882fb319c1660d2e8a08c66e688b4ca.avif?t=1770201688 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Arcade-Style Speed:</strong> Feel the thrill of ultra-fast races with tight controls and fluid handling.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Stunning Tracks:</strong> Compete across gravity-defying circuits on alien planets and neon-lit mega-cities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Immersive Soundtrack</strong>: A pulsing electronic score fuels the action with energy and atmosphere.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unique Teams:</strong> Six rival teams with distinct visual identities and backstories.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3582420/extras/a54f267ba0c5845905058fcc6d96bd68.avif?t=1770201688\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3582420/extras_big/a54f267ba0c5845905058fcc6d96bd68.avif?t=1770201688 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Multiple Games Mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic races </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Time attack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grand Prix</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Career</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Player-Focused Development</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Millennium Runners is built with our community in mind. We share behind-the-scenes updates, early builds, and collect feedback directly from players. Help shape the future of the game and be part of something epic.  <br>  <br><strong>No gravity. No limits. Just drive. Only the best will join the legend.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Welcome to the Future of Anti-Gravity Racing</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Step into the cockpit of next-generation anti-gravity ships. In a world where speed rules all, only the fastest can claim glory in the Millennium Cup. Get ready for a high-stakes ride through stunning sci-fi tracks and intense team rivalries.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3582420/extras/8882fb319c1660d2e8a08c66e688b4ca.avif?t=1770201688\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3582420/extras_big/8882fb319c1660d2e8a08c66e688b4ca.avif?t=1770201688 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Arcade-Style Speed:</strong> Feel the thrill of ultra-fast races with tight controls and fluid handling.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Stunning Tracks:</strong> Compete across gravity-defying circuits on alien planets and neon-lit mega-cities.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Immersive Soundtrack</strong>: A pulsing electronic score fuels the action with energy and atmosphere.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unique Teams:</strong> Six rival teams with distinct visual identities and backstories.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3582420/extras/a54f267ba0c5845905058fcc6d96bd68.avif?t=1770201688\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3582420/extras_big/a54f267ba0c5845905058fcc6d96bd68.avif?t=1770201688 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Multiple Games Mode</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic races </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Time attack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grand Prix</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Career</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Player-Focused Development</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Millennium Runners is built with our community in mind. We share behind-the-scenes updates, early builds, and collect feedback directly from players. Help shape the future of the game and be part of something epic.  <br>  <br><strong>No gravity. No limits. Just drive. Only the best will join the legend.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
